{"tid":774863,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"單身圍爐取暖區","createTime":"2018-08-10T16:12:08.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-14T06:29:41.000Z","uid":132227,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"cde50eeeef990151b71b71716a3215d5a0037c9f","tid":774863,"uid":132227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-10T16:12:08.000Z","msg":"單身左年幾 覺得單身都幾好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n想訓晏教想打機想早訓想夜訓唔得閒覆電話乜鳩都唔洗諗人地感受<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n拍拖要顧慮太多嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n錢又洗得多<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲要對方一冷淡或者做啲咩就又亂諗嘢sad到仆街<br />\n諗諗下自己一個都幾自由幾舒服<br />\n有班朋友陪下自己癲都夠啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n再加上自己條件又唔係好 <br />\n搵個要接受到自己既人太難了<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n雖然有啱既對象都會忍唔住想拍拖。。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有冇單身柒頭入黎吹下水圍下爐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e497c80dc4d692c15a202cf699133f9cbb9f9e26","tid":774863,"uid":198583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-10T16:13:30.000Z","msg":"幾歲"},{"pid":"cc4b56bbfd536f9483b3717241db80966166472f","tid":774863,"uid":132227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e497c80dc4d692c15a202cf699133f9cbb9f9e26","tid":774863,"uid":198583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-10T16:13:30.000Z","msg":"幾歲"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-10T16:15:08.000Z","msg":"廿頭"},{"pid":"bc8e55af740bf5ed3c7da98aa4b9d7e9fa247a24","tid":774863,"uid":180073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-10T18:02:28.000Z","msg":"單身狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其實我都唔想做   完<br />\n晚安"},{"pid":"c50e426248971beb00b1df21d7c0568a337a8016","tid":774863,"uid":132227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bc8e5